FT  18 JAN 94 / World Trade News: ABB in Dollars 100m Leipzig deal
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By IAN RODGER
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
   ZURICH
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
ABB Asea Brown Boveri, the leading power engineering group, has won an order
worth more than Dollars 100m (Pounds 67.5m) for a combined heat and power
plant at Gera near Leipzig, reports Ian Rodger in Zurich.
The order, from Kraftwerke Gera, is the seventh ABB has received for
