<HEADLINE>
FT  17 JAN 94 / Observer: Fourth dimension
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Some companies haven't quite got their globalisation act together yet.
Telecommunications giant AT&amp;T is running an advertisement - 'travel in a
world without borders, time zones or language barriers' - which places
Surinam in Africa. That's breaking down borders with a vengeance; Surinam
sits in Latin America.
</TEXT>
